Package: ggdmcPrior
Type: Package
Title: ggdmc module for standard and truncated distributions
Version: 0.2.8.9
Date: 2024-06-26
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Yi-Shin", family = "Lin", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "yishinlin001@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Yi-Shin Lin <yishinlin001@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions for specifying and evaluating 
    standard and truncated distributions, designed to work with the ggdmc 
    package. It supports Bayesian computation and includes utilities 
    for density calculation, sampling, and visualisation.
